        public Event​(java.lang.String id,
             java.lang.String descendant,
             java.lang.String personId,
             float latitude,
             float longitude,
             java.lang.String country,
             java.lang.String city,
             java.lang.String type,
             int year)
        Creates a new Event.
        Parameters:
        id - a unique identifier for this event
        descendant - the username of the user in whose family map this event is found
        personId - the id of the person in whose life this event occurred
        latitude - the latitude at which the event occurred
        longitude - the longitude at which the event occurred
        country - the country in which the event occurred
        city - the city in which the event occurred
        type - the event's type (e.g., birth, baptism, marriage, etc.)
        year - the year in which the event occurred
